Class GroupPathElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • saf.core.ui.dock.GroupPathElement

  • public class GroupPathElement
extends java.lang.Object
    An element in a GroupPath. This defines the location and size of a group space with respect to its parent and can produce the correct CLocation.

    Nick Collier
